data.description: New Price in the Conservatory! You'll love this 2-Story Home in The Conservatory with 4 BRs and 4 BAs. Located on a corner lot of the Cul de Sac this home will meet all your desires. The main floor features an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings with an abundance of natural light from Southern exposure in the adjoined Living Rm and Dining Rm that flow into the Kitchen and Family Rm. The lg. eat-in kitchen has a breakfast island, access to the deck and backyard,  hardwood flooring, plantation shutters and plenty of counterspace and cabinetry. Enter the Family Rm with gas fireplace, built-ins and lots of windows facing the beautiful backyard. Head upstairs to find 3 Bedrooms. Huge Primary BR Suite boasts a 5 pc. Bath, separate sitting area with custom shelving and walk-in closet with built-ins. The second story is complete with 2 additional bedrooms, full bath and convenient laundry room. The fabulously fully finished basement with natural light and luxury vinyl flooring offers you many options, which includes a lg. 4th bedroom with French doors; sitting room and beautifully upgraded lg. 3/4 bath with oversized walk-in shower. Options could include In-law suite, home office, secondary family/game/entertainment area. The oversized garage also offers extra storage space. Make this house your home and see it today! Assumable loan at 2.635%! Inquire for more info.
